.TH "nfp_net_reconfig_post" 9 "nfp_net_reconfig_post" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nfp_net_reconfig_post \- Post async reconfig request
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nfp_net_reconfig_post
.BI "(struct nfp_net *nn "  ","
.BI "u32 update "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "nn" 12
NFP Net device to reconfigure
.IP "update" 12
The value for the update field in the BAR config
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Record FW reconfiguration request.  Reconfiguration will be kicked off
whenever reconfiguration machinery is idle.  Multiple requests can be
merged together!
